line" n="3">D</hi>ir passt) <date>Dienstag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Früh</time>.</p><closer>Herzlichst<lb/><signed>Richard</signed></closer></div></body><back><listPerson><tei:person xml:id="pmb10863">
